  "prompt": "Who are best packers and movers in Marathahalli?",
  "response": "To find the best packers and movers in Marathahalli, Bangalore, you can consider several factors such as customer reviews, services offered, pricing, and reliability. Some of the well-reviewed packers and movers in Marathahalli include:\n\n1. **Aadhunik Packers and Movers**: Known for their professional service and customer satisfaction.\n\n2. **Agarwal Packers and Movers**: A well-established name in the industry, offering various moving services with good customer reviews.\n\n3. **Safe Express Packers and Movers**: Trusted for their prompt service and careful handling of goods.\n\n4. **Leo Packers and Movers**: Offers a range of moving services and is reputed for reliability and efficiency.\n\n5. **VRL Movers and Packers**: Offers competitive pricing and a wide range of services with positive customer feedback.\n\nMake sure to check recent reviews and get quotes from multiple movers to find the one that best fits your needs.",
